    rdfs:label "The European Society of Cardiology" ;
    prop:extractedFrom """It also has value as a prognostic lab value in patients with atherosclerosis or coronary heart disease as its levels correlate with the severity of the illness.[63]
The European Society of Cardiology recently released a PCT-guided algorithm for administering antibiotics in patients with dyspnea and suspected acute heart failure.""" ;
    prop:release base:antibiotics ;
    prop:sourceUrl "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Procalcitonin"^^xsd:anyURI .

